    <div class="col-8">
        <h2>Welcome to the Western Sydney Hotel</h2>
        <div>
            <p>
               This is one of the biggest Hotel in the Sydney that we are built that consists of many good sites such as a delicious kind of food from many countries. The food makes by famous chefs that have high qualification in the world and not only that our hotel also has amazing views with rate 5 in the world that you can enjoy it with your family and friends. We provide good services to meet your criteria.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
        <h2>Useful Links</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://www.diningroom.com.au/"> Dining Room </a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/sydcf-four-points-sydney-central-park?program=spg"> Views from hotel </a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.fourseasons.com/sydney/accommodations/#guest_rooms"> Luxury Rooms </a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.shangri-la.com/sydney/shangrila/rooms-suites/"> Standard King Rooms </a></li>
        </ul>
        
    </div>
</div>